reviewText: I picked up a copy of this at a teaching seminar at the Bob Bullock Museum in Austin, TX.  I LOVE IT so much!!!  I show it to my kids every year in my classroom.  They always grown when it starts but they really get into it and they love it.  I wish I could get newer, different episodes.  Love it!

Really Do Enjoy How It Captures The Passion Of These Talented Young Musicians, Really Enjoy The Variety Of Conjunto, Cajun And Polka Music It Is All Very Lively. A Really Enjoyable Program, Glad To Add This DVD To My Collection,  It Will Really Be Treasured For Sure!
